    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">14 ёшдан 18 ёшгача бўлган меросхўрнинг мерос мол-мулкни қабул қилиш тўғрисидаги аризаси</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Аризани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора номи ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Ариза келиб тушган сана </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Ариза келиб тушган сана </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мерос иши № </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Мерос иши рақами </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Ариза берувчи онасининг манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> онам </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ариза берувчининг онаси Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> (Паспорт: </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Ариза берувчи онасининг паспорт серияси ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Ариза берувчининг онасига паспорт берган ИИБ номи </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Ариза берувчининг онасига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган) розилиги</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">ва унинг иштирокида ҳаракат қилувчи фарзанди </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Ариза берувчининг манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> томонидан </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> (Паспорт: </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Ариза берувчининг паспорт серияси ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Ариза берувчига паспорт берган ИИБ номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#19}Ариза берувчига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">АРИЗА</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза тузилган жой </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза тузилган сана</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Менинг отам </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#22}Ариза берувчи отасининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#23}Ариза беруви отасининг яшаган манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> манзилида доимий равишда яшаб келиб, </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#24}Ариза берувининг отаси вафот этган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда вафот этди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Унинг ўлимидан сўнг мерос мол-мулк сифатида </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#25}Мерос – мол-мулки жойлашган манзил </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> манзилида жойлашган уй-жой ҳамда </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#26}Мерос бўлиб қолган автотранспорт воситасини рўйхатга олган ИИБ ЙХХБ ТРИБ </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ИИБ ЙХХБ ТРИқБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#27}Мерос бўлиб қолган автотранспорт воситасига транспорт воситасини қайд этиш гувоҳномасига берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган № </span><span class=\"structures structure-28\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#28}Автотранспорт воситасини қайд этиш гувоҳномасининг рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> рақамли транспорт воситасини қайд этиш гувоҳномасига эга бўлган </span><span class=\"structures structure-29\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#29}Автотранспорт русуми </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> русумли, </span><span class=\"structures structure-30\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#30}Автотранспорт воситаси ишлаб чиқарилган йил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда ишлаб чиқарилган, давлат рақами белгиси </span><span class=\"structures structure-31\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#31}Автотранспорт воситасининг давлат рақам белгиси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> бўлган автотранспорт воситаси қолди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 1135-моддасига асосан юқорида кўрсатилган мерос мол-мулкка биздан бошқа қонун бўйича биринчи навбатдаги меросхўрлар, яъни марҳумнинг болалари </span><span class=\"structures structure-32\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#32}Марҳумнинг бошқа фарзандларининг Ф.И.О.лари </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> бор.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Юқорида кўрсатилган мерос мол-мулкка нисбатан бизларга қонун бўйича меросга бўлган ҳуқуқ тўғрисидаги гувоҳнома беришингизни сўраймиз.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Биз меросхўрларни яширганлик оқибатлари ва жавобгарлик ҳақида огоҳлантирилдик.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">2. Мен- </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ариза берувчининг онаси Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> марҳум турмуш ўртоғим </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#22}Ариза берувчи отасининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> билан биргаликда никоҳимиз давомида орттирилган ва унинг номига расмийлаштирилган умумий мол-мулкнинг 1/2 улушига нисбатан мулк ҳуқуқи тўғрисида гувоҳнома олишни хоҳламайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Аризага қуйидаги ҳужжатларни илова қиламиз:</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">1. Марҳумнинг ўлим ҳақидаги гувоҳнома нусхаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">2. Никоҳ тузилганлиги ҳақидаги гувоҳнома нусхаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">3. Туғилганлик ҳақидаги гувоҳномалар нусхалари</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">4. Марҳумнинг турар жойидан маълумотнома.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">5. Автотранспорт воситасини қайд этиш гувоҳномаси нусхаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">6. АТВ баҳолаш тўғрисида экспертиза хулосаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span class=\"structures structure-33\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#33}Аризага илова қилинаётган бошқа ҳужжатлар </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">ИМЗОЛАР:</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ариза берувчининг онаси Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ______________</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Имзо</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">2. Онам иштирокида ва розилиги билан имзо қўйдим: </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ______________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Имзо</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ариза берувчининг онаси Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг шахси </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Ариза берувчининг онасига п